lead_paragraph: Dalian Wanda, the Chinese conglomerate that owns the AMC movie theater chain and nurtures Hollywood ambitions, has sometimes turned to the secretive business network of a politically connected Chinese billionaire in times of need.

abstract: The plan, which is meant to revive what was once the core of corporate activity in the city, is likely to make the area more densely packed while yielding upgrades to subway stations and public spaces.
snippet: The plan, which is meant to revive what was once the core of corporate activity in the city, is likely to make the area more densely packed while yielding upgrades to subway stations and public spaces.
lead_paragraph: The City Council on Wednesday unanimously approved a rezoning for a section of Midtown Manhattan that is likely to make the area even more densely packed with high-rise office buildings but that promises to yield improvements to subway stations and public spaces.

abstract: The mayor’s proposal, meant to provide long-term funding for the subway, also deflected attention from controversies involving his political donors.
snippet: The mayor’s proposal, meant to provide long-term funding for the subway, also deflected attention from controversies involving his political donors.
lead_paragraph: Mayor Bill de Blasio had just unveiled his plan on Monday to tax wealthy New Yorkers and direct the funds to the ailing subway system and its lowest-income riders when the protest signs came out. Not outside the site, but facing Mr. de Blasio at the lectern.

headline_main: De Blasio’s Push for Tax on Wealthy Helps Put Pressure on Cuomo
headline_print_headline: Mayor’s Push for Tax on Wealthy Helps Put Pressure on Cuomo

abstract: The mayor will announce a proposal for a tax on New York City residents who earn more than $500,000 to raise money for subway and bus improvements.
snippet: The mayor will announce a proposal for a tax on New York City residents who earn more than $500,000 to raise money for subway and bus improvements.
lead_paragraph: Mayor Bill de Blasio plans to push for a tax on wealthy New Yorkers to pay for improvements needed to address the crisis engulfing New York City’s subway, city officials said on Sunday.

abstract: The payroll processor is the latest company in the sights of ever-bolder financiers aiming to reshape businesses to bolster stock prices.
snippet: The payroll processor is the latest company in the sights of ever-bolder financiers aiming to reshape businesses to bolster stock prices.
lead_paragraph: ADP, the payroll processing giant, said on Friday that the hedge fund mogul William A. Ackman had sought five seats on its 10-member board, in the latest clash between corporate America and activist investors.

abstract: Moving past the dramatic ouster of the financier-turned-spokesman, the White House picked up its campaign for tax changes. But challenges await.
snippet: Moving past the dramatic ouster of the financier-turned-spokesman, the White House picked up its campaign for tax changes. But challenges await.
lead_paragraph: Anthony Scaramucci, the voluble financier turned colorful communications director, is out of the White House.
